  "id": "RAW_d406a94a",
  "title": "爆火 3 天、被投资人追捧，「死了么」正式出海",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650676652&idx=1&sn=8d88e1c5aaa3bf041f9366421d37132f",
  "date": "2026-01-14 13:14:00",
  "author": "白鲸出海",
  "siteName": "白鲸出海",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 4px;border-color: rgb(53, 175, 253);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLehjib7VguVwIcW2tBZ3fyuYE9yIzfZUOobQ0pibHuWTiaZZR9wBfz9fTQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"555\" data-cropsely2=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"503192986\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae9aac0c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLehjib7VguVwIcW2tBZ3fyuYE9yIzfZUOobQ0pibHuWTiaZZR9wBfz9fTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">同一个世界，同一种焦虑。</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -1px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 1px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(134, 147, 155);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">封面图片由AI生成</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">出品</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜白鲸出海编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">作者</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜张凯然</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">编辑</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜殷观晓</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1 月 10 日，一款名为「死了么」的付费 App 冲上了 iOS 付费下载榜的榜首（最初售价 1 元，目前已经涨至 8 元，海外各市场售价基本在 1 美元左右），并且已经霸榜 3 天，根据点点数据，1 月 10 日和 &nbsp;11 日，「死了么」的全球下载量分别为 2289 和 2279，但根据创始人的说法，这个数字是被大大低估了的，他透露，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">目前日新增用户是爆火前的 500 倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而在爆火 3 天后，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">这款产品宣布国内与海外的名字统一改成「Demumu」</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，从名字来看，「死了么」显然是在参考「饿了么」，而根据媒体的解读，新的英文名「Demumu」，可能是「Death+Labubu」融合的产物，借助「Labubu」在海外的超高影响力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一大片“死了么”中，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">被“眷顾”的 3 个 95 后</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「死了么」最初于 2025 年 6 月上线，免费使用，后续才转为付费下载。它的界面和功能相当简单，用户首次打开应用时，输入自己的姓名和紧急联系人邮箱，然后只需每天点击绿色按钮进行签到；服务需求也很明确，证明自己还活着，如果用户连续 2 天没有签到，系统就会以用户的名义向紧急联系人的邮箱发邮件求救。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">选择邮件，很有可能是为了规避短信或微信的合规门槛，但说实话，按照笔者看邮箱的频率，如果我的朋友通过这种方式求救，可能早就凉透了……</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片1 (2).png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5604166666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"480\" data-imgfileid=\"503192989\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=add33ad3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLia3FAqoJNKGTQA1k5oeMN5UGOgRg1vzZ0XJf0jibFCvVccChv8WbBMjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其创始人透露，团队一共有 3 个人，都是兼职且远程交互，产品的开发成本大约 200 美元。但「死了么」火起来是在产品上线的半年后，其实，在这个时间点，市场上已经有很多类似产品，也不乏产品设计更成熟的 App，而在「死了么」爆火后，搞抽象的同类竞品更是泛滥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">唯独「死了么」被流量与投资人眷顾，与其说是产品有什么亮点，不如说是这个自带流量的名字、以及小红书上被突然 cue 带来的泼天流量。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">团队的执行力之外，其他的成功因素，都充满了偶然性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">例如，「死了么」的名字，最早可能源于其他开发者，根据微信公众号上的可查信息，最早有这个 Idea 并公之于众的，是运营公众号「饼干哥哥 AGI」的开发者，他在 2025年3月就完成了产品的起名和原型设计，但并没有上线，被网友嘲讽错失 1000 万。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片 1.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0485436893203883\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"309\" data-imgfileid=\"503192990\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75e0f541&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLR3vhGk9mLEFlFEQp7Nv4OuvcWsn4of5ydnsfMwtJ0TcJDicgeuCUKMg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">饼干哥哥 AGI 2025年3月就写</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">文章，将这款 App 作为开发案例分享</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该开发者也自嘲，最终是没有看懂这个抽象的世界。但「死了么」团队却真的将 App 上架并完成了上述成绩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不得不说，在成功背后，除了团队执行力超强，也有其他必然因素---真实的社会困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 5 []\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">流量随机，需求真实，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">同一个世界、同样的焦虑</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">过去几十年中，中国家庭的平均规模急剧缩小。根据 2020 年全国人口普查，全国一共有 25.4% 的一人家庭，远高于十年前的 14.5%。虽然在这其中，独居老人显然更需要这种“证明自己还活着”的服务，但数据显示，一二线城市独居的年轻人的数量也在快速提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.615\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"800\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLTWk9kia2TgLFSV6zaVIWqrSDYP7FtLAOFXEG60vFMTibQqxSTTWPu8Mw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"1428\" data-imgfileid=\"503192994\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e33d95e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLTWk9kia2TgLFSV6zaVIWqrSDYP7FtLAOFXEG60vFMTibQqxSTTWPu8Mw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">根据澎湃新闻的调查数据，2010 年，这个人群只有 1800 万左右，而到了 2030年，这个数字就将达到 4000-7000 万，随着数量提升，独居年轻人的“安全焦虑”也与日俱增。一位下载了「死了么」的国内用户表示：“我担心如果我出了什么事，可能会独自死在出租屋内，而且没人会知道，这就是我下载这个应用的原因。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"image.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7888888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"503192992\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=05e96a43&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLpXBwRge1cDrtNUB5fTL1FcruwJb2V8nPvSzqJGhVAEeX9XZ9lMCPAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">「死了么」最初应该是全球同步上线，改名「Demumu」是其释放正式出海新号的一个节点。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">笔者分别在中国与英国区的 iOS 端购买并下载了这款产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在国内，这款产品叫「死了么」，而在海外，已经改名为「Demumu」，但在中文系统中，无论从哪个应用商店下载，产品名仍是「死了么」，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">界面与功能，国内外也没有任何区别，除了名字以外，团队可能还没来及进行海外市场的“本地化”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">成绩上，「Demumu」登上了几个发达国家的付费下载榜前列，美国付费榜的排名在 25，单日下载量应该在几百次左右，应该是海外华人或者留学生刷小红书后的贡献。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">虽然，传播链条可能依然没有传到到海外本土用户，但海外市场应同样具备爆火土壤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">根据世界卫生组织 （WHO）2025 年的相关报告，全球约有 1/6 的人受孤独困扰，而 15-24 岁年轻群体是重灾区。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">而在美国、日本等国家，结合居住方式、与既有的社会问题，独居人群，尤其是独居年轻人群的“安全焦虑”也越来越严重。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">比如在美国，年轻人主要居住在公寓当中，住户流动性很大，也缺乏“居委会”等组织对住户进行管理和服务，且美国年轻人毒品、药物、酒精滥用的情况越发普遍，独居患病或死亡的风险也更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而日韩等亚洲国家，也正因为严重的“空心化、少子化”， 面临日益严重的“独居安全挑战”。根据日本政府的调查显示，2024年，日本有 7.6 万独居者在家中去世，死亡 8 天以上才被发现的有 2.1 万人 （ 被定义为孤独死 ），而其中，40 岁以下孤独死的人数超过 1000，20 岁左右的案例数也超过 100，在日本，孤独死已经不是老人的专利了，日本部分公寓已经推出了“智能电力监控”系统，如果 24 小时内没有用电量变化就自动报警。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片4 (1).png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.79375\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"960\" data-imgfileid=\"503192993\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c0af0e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJzB4CZdSVVa11RXRkE42Xtsz6ibibQ5zLKwKZVmt8skO0nG6QMUibVfNibu7IS8ya84CLkDdSDGiat1EmSdaSfy9lg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">日本朝日新闻的类似报道</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而生育率更低的韩国“一人户”的比例也高的吓人，截止 2025 年底，韩国一人户已超 800 万，占总住户的 36% 以上，独居率远超国内。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">随着社会经济的发展，“社会原子化”是必然趋势，再加上很多发达国家都面临的“空心化、少子化”问题，至少从大趋势来看，「死了么」在海外，不乏用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 5 []\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">写在最后</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据《经济观察报》报道，1 月 10 日，「死了么」创始人原计划以 100 万元出让公司 10% 股份，若以此计算，这款产品的估值已达千万，但后续的 3 天内，就有 60 多个投资人找到创始团队，并提出投资意向，竞价后，融资额已上涨至近千万元级别，团队预计本周内敲定本轮融资。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">回顾「死了么」爆火到出海以及取得初步成绩、被投资人眷顾，团队最核心的可能就是超强的执行力，发现需求并真的上线。AI vibe coding 日益提升的能力正在助力更多开发者、甚至产品经理上线产品的能力，更难的在于发现真实需求。例如前面提到的最早开发「死了么」的饼干哥哥 AGI 是被小红书的“吐槽贴”激发灵感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「死了么」就像投向水面上的一颗石子，突然让大家意识到，存在着如此真实需求的大规模市场。但是，就像国内上线的各种抽象竞品一样，海外也必然快速充满了大量类似产品，其中不乏成熟的出海团队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这三位幸运的 95 后，能走多久，还充满了未知数。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:10px;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;overflow-y:auto;box-sizing:border-box;height:240px;\">\n     <div style=\"overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 78%;padding: 0px;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(107, 160, 172);text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考文章：</span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 12px;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">1、“死了么”App 爆火背后：流量来了，困境未解&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 8px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><a href=\"https://www.huxiu.com/article/4826217.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.huxiu.com/article/4826217.html</a></span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 8px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">2、China’s Hottest App Is a Daily Test of Whether You’re Still Alive</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 8px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/china-are-you-dead-yet-app/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/china-are-you-dead-yet-app/</a></span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 8px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">3、“死了么”：一款爆红的中国独居年轻人热门应用程式</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 8px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\"><a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/articles/cqxy2jd33e2o/simp\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/articles/cqxy2jd33e2o/simp</a></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "一款名为“死了么”（Demumu）的付费 App 凭借其独特概念和迎合独居焦虑的社会需求，在爆火后迅速出海，并获得投资人青睐，体现了低成本开发与发现真实需求的重要性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "一款名为“死了么”（Demumu）的付费 App 凭借其独特概念和迎合独居焦虑的社会需求，在爆火后迅速出海，并获得投资人青睐，体现了低成本开发与发现真实需求的重要性。",
  "summary": "文章详细报道了名为“死了么”（现更名为“Demumu”）的付费 App 短时间内走红并获得投资人追捧的现象。它提供简单的“证明自己还活着”的签到功能，若用户连续两天未签到，则向紧急联系人发送求救邮件。文章分析了产品爆火的偶然性（名字、小红书流量）和必然性（社会独居焦虑，尤其是年轻人群体）。同时，文章指出，该产品迅速出海并在发达国家付费榜上占得一席之地，这背后是全球范围内普遍存在的独居和孤独问题。最后，文章探讨了低成本高效率的开发模式（AI 辅助编程）和发现真实需求的重要性，并对这款产品的未来发展持观望态度。",
  "mainPoints": [
